spec_data.Name: NetworkManager-glib-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the header and pkg-config files for development
applications using NetworkManager functionality from applications that
use glib.
This is the older NetworkManager API.  See also NetworkManager-libnm-devel.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 27 Sep 2017 01:03:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Header files for adding NetworkManager support to applications (old API).
